#adjusted this and other plots to forgo seasonal facet wrap so that we can have
#a better sample size and added geom_smooth() method - A. Warren
teams_train%>%
  ggplot(mapping = aes(x =mean_iso , y = win_rate))+
    geom_point(size = 1.2, alpha = 0.35)+
    geom_smooth(method = "lm")
## `geom_smooth()` using formula 'y ~ x'

iso_fit <- linear_reg() %>%
  set_engine("lm") %>%
  fit(win_rate ~ mean_iso, data = teams_train)
tidy(iso_fit)
